import React, {useState} from "react"; import {useNavigate} from "react-router-dom"; import axios from "axios" const AddEmployee = () => { const navigate = useNavigate() const [employee, setEmployee] = useState({ user_id: "", work_email: "", f_name: "", m_name: "", s_name: "", personal_email: "", contact_num: 0, dob: "", p_address: "", c_address: "", date_hired: "", sex: "", created_by: "", updated_by: "", }); const handleChange = (e) => { setEmployee(prev => ({ ...prev, [e.target.name]: e.target.value})) } const handleClick = async e => { e.preventDefault() try{ await axios.post("http://localhost:6197/addEmployee", employee) navigate("/employees") } catch(err){ } } return(
